{"tid":1255440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心淡既人唔好灰心","createTime":"2019-06-24T13:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T13:44:06.000Z","uid":267749,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87c8ac3185e6f38a35060489c80e1c78cedc15bc","tid":1255440,"uid":267749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:31:04.000Z","msg":"發夢69隻手受左傷到依家仲痛緊，夜晚舊狗署又畀人抄ID同影相。612，613朝早落住雨都跑去金鐘，之後因為要去外地做野走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n係外國見住唔少&quot;香港&quot;市民616食盡催淚彈、橡膠子彈、布袋彈，用血汗換黎既只有林鄭所謂既道歉及&quot;理解&quot;。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n場杖耐左，林鄭一路拖，最後我地只會慢慢分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線心理上覺得被賣當Condom、和理非無用，生理上身體又受盡痛苦。<br />\n後勤可能晒左好多錢，走遍港九新界只為買物資畀前線。<br />\n文宣仲要一有突發就要整圖打文，２４小時ｍｏｎ撚住最新消息<br />\n我作為前線一員，無可否認的確有啲心淡。但就係咁我先要出POST去鼓勵自己，鼓勵其他人。<br />\n如果唔咁做最後既贏家只會係林鄭同埋中國。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地６月２６日，一定要企出黎！<br />\n就算有幾心淡，有幾受委屈都要企出黎！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為我地場杖仲未完！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1bdDLW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1bdDLW.png&h=9938a348&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fabda7a3fc974e4cbf2708b6bc7442df7ce8bd52","tid":1255440,"uid":267749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc39fda9531de6024966b0b0ee417b04f02fb719","tid":1255440,"uid":267749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350f9f72d99c1ab8f026f7327f05a90d3cc61185","tid":1255440,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:33:39.000Z","msg":"&quot;616食盡催淚彈、橡膠子彈、布袋彈&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咩事???"},{"pid":"923d7b3c9e9346129f9a1265353eef3bea5ce42f","tid":1255440,"uid":230730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:34:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6851b52b598ed45d16c2e929c2debe1e6da63537","tid":1255440,"uid":267749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:35:19.000Z","msg":"612 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a4820c794e0f74e0963448b62c1b42e4f6ccc8","tid":1255440,"uid":267749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"紅都面埋"},{"pid":"76c078acca8958bf589dc738d04a5639aff6ddd5","tid":1255440,"uid":267749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:38:20.000Z","msg":"柒左都照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdab3b2dc5dbbf6e552b4f315be0847aa7d4cc8","tid":1255440,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:39:01.000Z","msg":"又分化？"},{"pid":"46750b6da3ee1bf8ecb8fec382f3f3e3c314f9fd","tid":1255440,"uid":29302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"1eb26cbb6e5b953e87e8a93e6b9d9be2e070166c","tid":1255440,"uid":260181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">625晚放工後去鰂魚涌社區會堂涼冷氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n嚟緊區選睇怕又有DQ<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1253306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/125